{"tid":1412723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推上國際】警方拘捕女示威者致內褲鬆脫　葉蘊儀譴責性暴力：侮辱女性可恥","createTime":"2019-08-05T07:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T12:32:58.000Z","uid":66271,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"52739eb87b1b40f37331f171e2535f50f997ff8f","tid":1412723,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2415000/2419234/yip_thumb_20190805_S_v2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2415000%2F2419234%2Fyip_thumb_20190805_S_v2_1024.jpg&h=8de306a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天水圍警署昨晚 (4日)被示威者一度包圍，期間有一名女示威者被警員制服，多名防暴警將女示威者抬入警署，期間她内褲鬆脫導致走光，事件引起社會不少質疑聲音。不少藝人認為警方在處理手法不尊重女性，已為母親的葉蘊儀便在社交平台激動表示侮辱女性。<br />\n<br />\n葉蘊儀今早在社交平台留言，對有女示威者被警方扯下內褲一事，甚感憤怒，表示將對當事人帶來心理創傷，她寫道：<br />\n<br />\n我想問佢犯咗乜嘢法？連內褲都被脫，下體暴露在人群當中，在眾目睽睽攝影機四處的現場，警方有沒有想過當事人的心理創傷及陰影。<br />\n<br />\n想問為何不讓示威者先穿上褲子才帶上警車？我想示威者都有權把自己嘅衣服穿上，只是有些人想侮辱女性示威者，讓他們不敢再站出來吧，可恥！<br />\n<br />\n葉蘊儀並hastag了#保護香港女性 #侮辱女性可恥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2415000/2419234/gloria_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2415000%2F2419234%2Fgloria_1024.jpg&h=6f2fc2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時她又轉貼聲稱是天水圍少女的報平安帖文，及「譴責警察以性暴力鎮壓示威者」的聯署。<br />\n<br />\n另外，一向關心社會的徐天佑，亦對今早女示威者被警方拉扯下內褲一事感憤慨，斥警方行為粗暴。<br />\n<br />\n此外，今天向電台告假的主持朱薰，亦有關注特首早上記者會，並留言如果出來不是解決問題，而是令雙方更對立，就不要出來。"},{"pid":"09d65566f7537c6a6a40e63b76756670a5ac9843","tid":1412723,"uid":250444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:40:51.000Z","msg":"快啲推到個個都識呢招！<br />\n成日見到啲車撞啲小朋友，又咩都做唔到，好撚嬲😢😢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求救 ， 點解條車胎充唔到氣 ， 依家塞住左條馬路 ， 大波絲打在線等<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1409159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1409159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6757c174064d2fc5ae4f81fd70c9d95a9ea88ded","tid":1412723,"uid":24737,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:42:37.000Z","msg":"睇錯孽瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1a84f5d7884df3353c50100297ee58cf91e850","tid":1412723,"uid":3873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6757c174064d2fc5ae4f81fd70c9d95a9ea88ded","tid":1412723,"uid":24737,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:42:37.000Z","msg":"睇錯孽瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"屌 我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156dc1a1b3cd46fab31cd008b99f6a6da106f7c6","tid":1412723,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82456283ac5b75d5137e713043b38050383ba9e","tid":1412723,"uid":53726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca1a84f5d7884df3353c50100297ee58cf91e850","tid":1412723,"uid":3873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6757c174064d2fc5ae4f81fd70c9d95a9ea88ded","tid":1412723,"uid":24737,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:42:37.000Z","msg":"睇錯孽瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"屌 我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"孽瘤都不知幾想show比人睇"},{"pid":"68b323e49266b8d15025e2d4904486aef89758e2","tid":1412723,"uid":7656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"睇錯葉留淑儀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7e1c715d2fbe0415444ac885a575a912b966f3","tid":1412723,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:50:13.000Z","msg":"睇錯葉蘊儀"},{"pid":"f3dbe908509f46f7d1c960a62633a6f437a8120a","tid":1412723,"uid":48057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4de40988acd6cebfd2b6a4d31bd6958aa5b57a66","tid":1412723,"uid":280812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"570fce56e115cbc9c8d0f8a1b892fc715e4899ac","tid":1412723,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:54:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a91826b28a0893617ff35d9765334ee8b0e96f48","tid":1412723,"uid":185289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"女權人士何在"},{"pid":"93329b8ab3da47a77eb38586840aa07ae778a382","tid":1412723,"uid":297642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:22:13.000Z","msg":"葛博士仲唔出黎譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d093fd42aa844ae0d8663369413b461b8e6d1fe1","tid":1412723,"uid":277649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:32:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">侮辱女性可恥</span></span>"}]}